BUGS

This library is a work of progress and not finished yet. But is full
usuable with the available widgets. It is already used for the GUIs in 
the develop version of Fvwm-Nightshade. So, if someone want to play with
it, you're welcome. Please send me bug reports or suggestions for 
improvements, thanks.

Send them to <t.funk@web.de>
